      "file_path": "vid-app-common/src/test/java/org/onap/vid/controllers/VidControllerTest.java",
      "patchset_number": 1,
      "line": 152,
      "message": "This model is really complicated. It has many dependencies and has a one to many relationship to other objects meaning it can be really huge. While having an empty model for test purposes may work, there is no reliance here on values that actually have information. Of course designing such a solution would require a lot of boilerplate code. Ideally the ServiceModel should be constructed from a source file which it represents (tosca?) using 3rd party libs and having a resource file. Please check if this can be somehow improved so that we can achieve a sweet spot between readability and a comprehensive test.",
